{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0001", "text": "茶 餘半杯早已漸冷 皺起眉頭喝下", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 4, 3, 9, 5, 2, 5, 4, 9, 0, 0, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["caa4", "jyu4", "bun3", "bui1", "zou2", "ji5", "zim6", "laang5", "zau3", "hei2", "mei4", "tau4", "hot3", "haa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "茶", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "餘", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "半杯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "早已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "漸冷", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "皺起", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "眉頭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喝下", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0002", "text": "我共你 在咖啡店中偶遇太驚訝", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 5, 2, 4, 3, 4, 3, 5, 2, 4, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "gung6", "nei5", "zoi6", "gaa3", "fe1", "dim3", "zung1", "ngau5", "jyu6", "taai3", "geng1", "ngaa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "共", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "咖啡店", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "中", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "偶遇", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "驚訝", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0003", "text": "還 談到天昏與地暗 未來和昨日", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 4, 3, 3, 5, 2, 4, 2, 0, 0, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waan4", "taam4", "dou3", "tin1", "fan1", "jyu5", "dei6", "am3", "mei6", "loi4", "wo4", "zok3", "jat6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "談到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天昏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "與", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地暗", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "和", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "昨日", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0004", "text": "你沒說 從眉梢已知你又再蜜運", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 4, 0, 0, 3, 5, 3, 5, 2, 4, 2, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "mut6", "syut3", "cung4", "mei4", "saau1", "ji5", "zi1", "nei5", "jau6", "zoi3", "mat6", "wan6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "從", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "眉梢", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "蜜運", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0005", "text": "我 也在當天差半分 愛上這人", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 2, 3, 3, 4, 3, 4, 5, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "jaa5", "zoi6", "tin1", "caa1", "bun3", "fan1", "oi3", "ze5", "jan4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "當天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "差", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "半分", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這人", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0006", "text": "妨礙是我心底那傲氣 難成全一吻", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 2, 5, 3, 9, 5, 2, 4, 0, 0, 0, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["fong4", "ngoi6", "si6", "ngo5", "sam1", "dai2", "naa5", "ngou6", "hei3", "naan4", "sing4", "cyun4", "jat1", "man5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "妨礙", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "心底", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "傲氣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "難", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "成全", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一吻", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0007", "text": "可笑嗎 還未完全放下", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 4, 3, 0, 2, 0, 0, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho2", "siu3", "maa1", "waan4", "mei6", "jyun4", "cyun4", "fong3", "haa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "可笑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "完全", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "放下", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0008", "text": "後悔不趁早 伸手挽着他", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 3, 4, 9, 3, 9, 5, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["hau6", "fui3", "bat1", "can3", "zou2", "san1", "sau2", "waan5", "zoek6", "taa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "後悔", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "趁早", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "伸手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "挽着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0009", "text": "才冷掉了熱茶", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 6}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 2, 5, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["coi4", "laang5", "diu6", "liu5", "jit6", "caa4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "才", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "冷掉", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "熱茶", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0010", "text": "可笑嗎 不爽快下抉擇", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 4, 3, 3, 9, 4, 2, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho2", "siu3", "maa1", "bat1", "song2", "faai3", "haa6", "kyut3", "zaak6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "可笑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不爽快", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "下", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "抉擇", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0011", "text": "坐到花也枯 燭光耗盡嗎", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 3, 5, 3, 3, 3, 4, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["co5", "dou3", "faa1", "jaa5", "fu1", "zuk1", "gwong1", "hou3", "zeon6", "maa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "坐到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "花", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "枯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "燭光", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "耗盡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0012", "text": "覺悟已太遲 他的心已冷", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 4, 0, 3, 3, 3, 5, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gok3", "ng6", "ji5", "taai3", "ci4", "taa1", "dik1", "sam1", "ji5", "laang5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "覺悟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已太遲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "冷", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0013", "text": "糖 沉進杯底再耐也未能溶化吧", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 4, 3, 9, 4, 2, 5, 2, 0, 0, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["tong4", "cam4", "zeon3", "bui1", "dai2", "zoi3", "noi6", "jaa5", "mei6", "nang4", "jung4", "faa3", "baa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "糖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沉進", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "杯底", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "耐", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "溶化", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0014", "text": "似是我 甜言聽了總會埋進心間", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 5, 0, 0, 3, 5, 9, 0, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ci5", "si6", "ngo5", "tim4", "jin4", "ting1", "liu5", "zung2", "maai4", "zeon3", "sam1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "似是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "甜言", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "總會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "埋進", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "心間", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "紅茶易冷", "artists": ["鍾舒漫"], "lyricists": ["李峻一"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2566", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZKf6IiS5ryr_MjU2Ng_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
